text: Emmy Snook (born 4 October 1973) is an Australian rower. She competed in the women's coxless four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Perth, Western Australia
